      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "手つかずの場所だとこんな植生になるんだ、面白いわね",
      "startTime": 156.3792230287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "franさん、自然に興味があったんですね\n少し意外です",
      "startTime": 165.3333226522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
